### 10. Display job groups having total salary greater than max salary of managers

```sql id="e9q10"
SELECT JOB FROM Employee GROUP BY JOB HAVING SUM(SAL)>(SELECT MAX(SAL) FROM Employee WHERE JOB='MANAGER');
```
